<hr noshade size=4>
<font color="blue"><h2><u>About Virtual Classroom</u></h2></font>
<p>Virtual classroom is an online education where teacher and student are separated by time and space. Teacher provides course content through course management application, multimedia resources , the internet, video conferencing, etc.  Virtual classroom is a software created for educational purposes.It provides an environment where students and teachers
	interact with each other virtually and can share presentations,documents,pdf's,lectures and other essential documents pertaining to the topic.</p>
	
	
	
<font color="blue"><h2><u>What does virtual classroom consist of?</u></h2></font>
<p>Virtual classroom consists of a chat hangout,broadcasting api and a calender.
	A chat-hangout allows students to chat with teachers,post doubts & receive important documents.The hangout allows various students
	to express their opinions and post questions which might be beneficial for other students.<br>
	The broadcasting api enables us to use the above 3 options where we can have a video chat between students and teachers allowing a virtual
	environment to be created where teachers can teach students online.</p>


